asset.hookText: The life of a traveling pro surf dude gives you plenty of time to fart around, especially on long flights and layovers, and while in random countries. Nate Tyler put together this quick video in iMovie and made the sweet song to go along in Garage Band while he was in Japan. Hope you enjoy.
